(563, 'Bridge Event: Implementing a Data Literate Culture at the School and Teacher Levels', '', '', '2014-10-29', '2014-10-29', '2:30&ndash;4 p.m. CT', 'Webinar', '', '', '', '<p>This interactive webinar examines how to use data effectively at the school, classroom, and student levels&mdash;with a focus on the rural school setting. Dr. Ellen Mandinach, director of WestEd''s Data for Decisions Initiative, and Diana Nunnaley, director of TERC''s Using Data Initiative, discuss the systemic nature of implementing and embedding data use in day-to-day practice. The presentation draws from the IES practice guide <em>Using Student Achievement Data to Support Instructional Decision Making</em>.</p>', '', '', '', '', 'Data Use, Rural, ', '', 'jwackwit', '2014-12-05', 'yes', 'yes', 'AR, EE, EL, LA, NM-AG, NM-PK, OK, ', 'http://relsouthwest.sedl.org/bridge_events/2014-10-29_datalit/index.html', 'no', '', ''),
(564, 'Bridge Event: Implementation of New Educator Evaluation Systems: Lessons Learned', '', '', '2014-11-03', '2014-11-03', '3&ndash;4:30 p.m. CT', 'Webinar', '', '', '', 'This interactive webinar examines the implementation of new state educator evaluation systems. Learn from the latest research and the experiences of other states as leading experts explore strategies and lessons learned. Gain insight into the issues state education leaders and policymakers should consider as they design, implement, and evaluate their new systems.', '', '', '', '', 'Educator Effectiveness, ', '', 'jwackwit', '2014-11-04', 'yes', 'yes', 'AR, EE, EL, LA, NM-AG, OK, TX, ', 'http://relsouthwest.sedl.org/bridge_events/2014-11-03_eesyst/index.html', 'no', '', ''),
